Actions.Text: REFERRED TO INVESTIGATIONS AND GOVERNMENT OPERATIONS
REFERRED TO INVESTIGATIONS AND GOVERNMENT OPERATIONS

Title: Prohibits the placement of liquor and/or wine within five feet of nonalcoholic beverages
Summary: Prohibits the placement of liquor and/or wine for sale within five feet of nonalcoholic beverages for retail licensees who sell such liquor and/or wine for consumption off premises.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the alcoholic beverage control law, in relation to requiring five feet of distance between alcoholic and nonalcoholic beverages
